{
  "policy": {
    "name": "alb-outdated-ssl-policy",
    "resource": "aws.app-elb",
    "description": "Detect ALBs not using the latest predefined security policy (ELBSecurityPolicy-TLS13-1-2-2021-06)",
    "filters": [
      {
        "type": "listener",
        "key": "Protocol",
        "value": "HTTPS"
      },
      {
        "type": "listener",
        "key": "SslPolicy",
        "value": "ELBSecurityPolicy-TLS13-1-2-2021-06",
        "op": "ne"
      }
    ],
    "actions": [
      {
        "type": "notify",
        "template": "default.html",
        "priority_header": "2",
        "subject": "\u26a0\ufe0f ALB Using Outdated SSL Policy - {{ region }}",
        "violation_desc": "**Application Load Balancer Using Outdated SSL/TLS Policy**\n\n**Load Balancer:** { resource.LoadBalancerName }\n**Current SSL Policy:** { resource.Listeners[?Protocol=='HTTPS'].SslPolicy | [0] }\n**Recommended:** ELBSecurityPolicy-TLS13-1-2-2021-06\n\n**Remediation:**\n```bash\naws elbv2 modify-listener \\\n  --listener-arn <listener-arn> \\\n  --ssl-policy ELBSecurityPolicy-TLS13-1-2-2021-06\n```\n",
        "to": [
          "security-team@company.com"
        ],
        "transport": {
          "type": "sqs",
          "queue": "https://sqs.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/172327596604/custodian-mailer-queue"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
